Operations Dashboard for ArcGIS is a configurable web app that provides location-aware data visualization and analytics for a real-time operational view of people, 
services, assets, and events. From a dynamic dashboard, view the activities and key performance indicators most vital to meeting your organization's objectives.
TASKS
Create a dashboard
Add elements
Set layout
Build interactivity
Save, test, and share

